author: Anthony Deaton
text: SO what I’m getting at is to just help your partners how you’d want to be helped. Give it all you’ve got. Love till you have nothing left to love for. It always pays you back in the end and I will never regret giving my entire self to someone who truly deserves it.

author: Anthony Deaton
text: No passive aggressive comments, no bullshit, just open minds. We take care of each other in a way I’ve never understood. He’s the man I’ve needed for a long time. Someone who understands what I’m dealing with, but never clouds over it with his own issues and vice versa.

author: Anthony Deaton
text: Also feeding THEIR mental health needs is something I’ve been learning to do better. I show him the appreciation he truly deserves and we thrive together. We openly communicate and never raise our voices. We have taught each other the true meaning of clear healthy communication.

author: Anthony Deaton
text: Being blinded by rage and hate does a lot to a person. I destroy, I break, and I fuck up a lot. I never mean to do these things, but they sometimes just happen. Having someone who understands my mental health and feeds it appropriately is so fucking helpful tho. He’s a keeper❤️🌈
